	Hi, I'm Nora aka Noz!

I am the baker, decorator and creative mind behind Baked by Noz. What started as a 
special treat for my nephew's birthday in June of 2025 has grown into a business
that allows me to be a part of life's most special celebrations.

Every cookie is baked from scratch using quality ingredients and hand decorated with
care and attention to detail. I love turning ideas into edible works of art, whether
it's a child's favourite character, elegant wedding favours, personalised gifts or
branded corporate cookies. 

For me, it's about more than just making cookies, it's about creating something that
brings people together, starts conversations and becomes part of lasting memories. 
Seeing the excitement on my customers faces when they receive their order is one of 
the most rewarding parts of what I do. 

Thank you for supporting my small business. I am so grateful to be trusted with your
special moments and I can't wait to create something delicious just for you. 

With love, 
Nora x 
